{"tid":2184011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想食A酸求指教 有圖慎入","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T06:02:29.000Z","uid":312646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4eca40bf671f8578c589a4866e8f65fe3cfb9c22","tid":2184011,"uid":312646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:31:24.000Z","msg":"有無朋友仔同我一樣<br />\n塊臉好多封閉式粉刺暗粒<br />\n整極都整唔到岀黎<br />\n去做針清啲姐姐又話我好多暗粒<br />\n次次清到好痛，紅腫<br />\n但一好翻啲暗粒又岀翻黎<br />\n呢排仲成日生石頭瘡<br />\n好難整岀黎，搞好耐，又痛又醜樣<br />\n想試下食A酸<br />\n巴打絲打們有無好醫生推薦<br />\n我係窮JJ，希望唔洗太貴<br />\n大家討論吓<br />\n<br />\n圖：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSiRCru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSiRCru.png&h=18c848b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WcZUAda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWcZUAda.png&h=6acfb413&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOr4cZR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOr4cZR.png&h=db7063d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e851874110f1b1d76ffdaa5ef086d60f8a670f47","tid":2184011,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"有無做開護膚"},{"pid":"502ce6b115726df8f71b04ae815ee1f0495d5339","tid":2184011,"uid":312646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"見到自己咁多暗粒同暗瘡真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80a019f42498de34f4e9beb821ae1fdd71516ea","tid":2184011,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"康正"},{"pid":"2de7284effa92d5386f713f706b86db0d281c021","tid"